column5: We are off to Cliff Lake. 7 grown men like kids on the night before Christmas. Will have a report when we get back. Thank You everyone for the replies on previous posts and especially thank you to Silverwiskers for all the helpfull information.
Brian, or anyone else in your group, when you've recovered I'm dying for your report on one of my favorite lakes.Thanks.
looking forward to your report on the lake on the other side of 105..(from Cedar)
